# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a parachutist plunged to his death here sunday after his reserve parachute became entangled with a video camera strapped to his helmet , police spokesman captain dave harrington said .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "Dave"
                  :op2 "Harrington")
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG1 (p2 / police)
                  :ARG2 (c / captain)))
      :ARG1 (p3 / plunge-01
            :ARG1 p
            :ARG0-of (p4 / parachute-01))
      :ARG4 (d / die-01
            :ARG1 p)
      :location (h2 / here)
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / sunday))
      :time (a / after
            :op1 (e / entangle-01
                  :ARG1 p
                  :ARG2 (c2 / camera
                        :mod (v / video)
                        :ARG1-of (s3 / strap-01
                              :ARG2 (h3 / helmet
                                    :poss p))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok alexander solzhenitsyn , nobel prize-winning author and former dissident , said thursday that his eight-week journey across russia had shown him a country in a `` pit '' in danger of strangulation by `` the boa constrictor of crime , '' but still with enough spiritual health to give hope for revival .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "alexander"
                  :op2 "Santzhenitsyn")

                              :op1 "Nobel")))

                  :time (f / former)))
      :ARG1 (s2 / show-01
            :ARG0 (j / journey-01
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (c / country
                        :location (c2 / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Russia")))
                  :duration (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 8
                        :unit (w2 / week)))
            :ARG1 (c3 / country
                  :location (p3 / pit)
                  :ARG1-of (e / endanger-01
                        :ARG0 (s3 / strangulate-01
                              :ARG0 (c4 / constrictor
                                    :mod (c5 / crime-02)
                                    :mod (b / boa))
                              :ARG1 p)))
            :ARG2 p
            :concession (h / have-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (h2 / health
                        :mod (s4 / spiritual)
                        :ARG1-of (h3 / have-quant-91

                              :ARG6 (g / give-01
                                    :ARG0 p
                                    :ARG1 (h4 / hopeful-03
                                          :ARG0 p
                                          :ARG1 (r / revive-01
                                                :ARG1 p)))))
                  :mod (s5 / still)))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / thursday)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok some non-governmental organizations -lrb- ngos -rrb- say they have started mobilizing resources worth millions of dollars to assist zimbabwean government in this year 's drought relief program , a press report said today .

            :ARG0 (p / press))

            :ARG0 (o / organization
                  :quant (s3 / some)
                  :mod (g / government-organization
                        :polarity -
                        :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01)))
            :ARG1 (s4 / start-01
                  :ARG0 o
                  :ARG1 (m / mobilize-01
                        :ARG0 o
                        :ARG1 (r2 / resource
                              :ARG1-of (w / worth-01
                                    :ARG2 (m2 / multiple
                                          :op1 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                                                :quant 1000000
                                                :unit (d / dollar)))))
                        :purpose (a / assist-01
                              :ARG0 o
                              :ARG1 (g3 / government-organization
                                    :ARG0-of (g4 / govern-01
                                          :ARG1 (c / country
                                                :name (n / name
                                                      :op1 "Zimbabwe"))))
                              :ARG2 (p2 / program
                                    :topic (r3 / relieve-01
                                          :ARG1 (d2 / drought))
                                    :time (y / year
                                          :mod (t / this)))))))
      :time (t2 / today))

# ::id 3 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

            :mod (o / official))

                  :prep-with (r / rest
                        :part-of (w / world)))
            :ARG4 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (p / pound))
            :time (d3 / date-entity
                  :month 9)
            :ARG4 (m3 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (p2 / pound))
            :time (d4 / date-entity
                  :month 11)
            :ARG1-of (m4 / mean-01
                  :ARG2 (m5 / monetary-quantity
                        :quant 1000000000
                        :unit (d5 / dollar))))
      :time (d6 / date-entity
            :month 11))

                  :location (s / south)))
      :ARG2 (s2 / seek-01

            :ARG1 (c2 / clemency
                  :beneficiary (m / maid
                        :mod (c3 / country
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Filipino"))
                        :ARG0-of (f / face-01

      :manner (s4 / show-01
            :ARG1 (u2 / unity)
            :ARG1-of (r4 / rare-02)))

# ::id 5 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok a ##-year-old boy was charged with murder in canada , a pipe bomb was found in an oklahoma school and school districts across the nation were on heightened alert on thursday as bomb threats , talk of hit lists and fears of more violence in the wake of the littleton , colo. , massacre continued to ripple outward .

(m / multi-sentence
      :snt1 (c / charge-05
            :ARG1 (b / boy
                  :age (t / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 1
                        :unit (y / year)))

                  :ARG0 b)
            :location (s / state
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Canada")))
      :snt2 (a / alert-01
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (s2 / school
                        :location (s3 / state
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Oklahoma")))
                  :op2 (d / district
                        :mod (s4 / school)
                        :location (a3 / across
                              :op1 (n3 / nation))))
            :ARG1-of (h / heighten-01)
            :time (d2 / date-entity
                  :weekday (t2 / thursday))
            :ARG1-of (c2 / cause-01
                  :ARG0 (c3 / continue-01
                        :ARG1 (a4 / and
                              :op1 (t3 / threaten-01
                                    :ARG1 (b2 / bomb))
                              :op2 (t4 / talk-01
                                    :ARG1 (l / list-01
                                          :ARG1 (h2 / hit-01)))
                              :op3 (f / fear-01
                                    :ARG1 (v / violence
                                          :mod (m3 / more)))
                              :time (w / wake
                                    :mod (l2 / littleton)))))))

            :ARG1 (p2 / project

                                    :op1 "Eu"))))))

                              :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Serbia"))))))
      :ARG1 (p2 / propose-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (l2 / legislate-01
                  :ARG1 (p3 / place-01
                        :ARG1 (m2 / military
                              :poss c2
                              :ARG0-of (d / depend-01
                                    :polarity -
                                    :mod (t / tradition)))
                        :ARG2 (c3 / control-01

                              :ARG1 m2
                              :ARG1-of (h2 / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG2 (g / great)
                                    :ARG3 (m3 / more))))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (s2 / sunday)))

                        :op2 "Choo")

                        :ARG1 (s2 / shoe))
                  :mod (l2 / luxury)
                  :poss-of (t / thing
                        :ARG1-of (c / create-01)
                        :ARG1-of (c2 / covet-01
                              :ARG0 (f2 / fashionista
                                    :location (w / worldwide)))))
            :ARG1 (r / range
                  :purpose (h / high-street)
                  :ARG1-of (s3 / sell-01
                        :location (s4 / store
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "H&amp;m")
                              :mod (c3 / chain)
                              :mod (c4 / country
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Sweden"))))))
      :time (w2 / wednesday))

                        :quant 5))

                  :mod (m / main))

# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (n / newspaper
            :name (n2 / name
                  :op1 "York"
                  :op2 "Times")
            :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01))
      :ARG1 (s2 / say-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 (m / military
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Army"))
                        :ARG2 (g / general
                              :ARG1-of (r / reserve-01)))
                  :poss (p2 / person
                        :ARG0-of h
                        :ARG2 (s3 / soldier))
                  :ARG1-of (p3 / photograph-01
                        :ARG2 (a / abuse-01
                              :ARG0 p2
                              :ARG1 (p4 / person
                                    :ARG1-of (ii / imprison-01
                                          :location (c / country
                                                :name (n5 / name
                                                      :op1 "Iraq"))))))))
      :ARG1 (c2 / control-01
            :ARG0 (ii2 / intelligence
                  :mod (m2 / military))
            :ARG1 (b / block
                  :mod (p5 / prison)
                  :ARG1-of (ii3 / involve-01))
            :ARG1-of (t / tight-05)
            :ARG0-of (e / encourage-01
                  :ARG2 a
                  :ARG1-of (p6 / possible-01)))
      :time (d / date-entity
            :weekday (s4 / saturday)))

                                    :ARG1 c
                                    :ARG2 (o / official)))))))

                        :topic (ii / import-01

                        :poss c)

                        :op1 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                              :quant 9000000000
                              :unit (d / dollar)))
                  :time (y / year
                        :mod (f / finance)
                        :mod (c2 / current))))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (m3 / monday)))

                                    :op1 "China"))

                  :time (t / today)))
      :op2 (c2 / call-03
            :ARG0 p

                        :mod c)
                  :ARG1 (n3 / negotiate-01
                        :ARG0 a2
                        :ARG2 (c3 / cross-02

                        :time (e2 / early))
                  :ARG1-of (p3 / practical-02))
            :ARG2 a2))
